    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Adherents of the College of Eloquence master the art of oratory. Persuasion is regarded as a high art, and a well-reasoned, well-spoken argument often proves more powerful than objective truth. These bards wield a blend of logic and theatrical wordplay, winning over skeptics and detractors with logical arguments, and plucking at heartstrings to appeal to the emotions of entire audiences.</p>\n<h3>College of Eloquence Features</h3>\n<p>3rd Level: @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.0BWmMnRrnEpQd9DB]{Silver Tongue}, @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.0LdSLkrqY3h78lOo]{Unsettling Words}</p>\n<p>6th Level: @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.2Yt03TvTL1Xh1Q0s]{Unfailing Inspiration}, @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.djwIWKX5cjB8Z0sl]{Universal Speech}</p>\n<p>14th Level: @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.mJSGhQ7R8B7etHD3]{Infectious Inspiration}</p>",
